                <a href="#item-1" class="control-button">.</a>
                <a href="#item-2" class="control-button">.</a>
                <a href="#item-3" class="control-button">.</a>
            </div>

        </div>

		<div class="description-single-project">

			<p>
				this project was part of the user interface subject, within the digital design course at the faculty of fine arts of the university of lisbon. the objective was to create an app from scratch, taking into consideration the entire creation of the design system, concept, development of wireframes, and high-fidelity mockups.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				<strong>project name:</strong> buddy walkies<br>
				<strong>institution:</strong> faculty of fine arts, university of lisbon<br>
				<strong>areas of exploration:</strong>research, benchmarking, interface design, design system, wireframes, mockup, prototype<br>
				<strong>year of completion:</strong> 2024<br>
				<strong>notes:</strong> group work with two other classmates
			</p>

			

		</div>

	</div>
	
	
    <Footer />
  
		
